---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="See what we may do with your data">
    <main
        class="flex flex-col justify-center mt-5 items-center overflow-x-hidden xl:left-7 mx-auto"
    >
        <div
            class="lg:py-5 lg:space-y-8 max-w-5xl px-2 py-3 sm:px-8 sm:py-12 sm:space-y-6 space-y-4 w-full"
        >
            <div
                class="flex flex-col p-5 rounded-2xl text-lg shadow-md bg-white dark:text-dark_mode_text dark:bg-dark_mode_post font-bold"
            >
                <p class="">
                    Privacy Policy - <a href="/" class="underline"
                        >https://chark1es.dev</a
                    >
                </p>
                <span class="text-sm font-normal"
                    >Effective Date: September 6, 2023</span
                >

                <span
                    class="text-sm mt-5 font-normal dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >At https://chark1es.dev, we value your privacy and are
                    committed to protecting the personal information you provide
                    when using our website. This Privacy Policy ("Policy")
                    explains how we collect, use, and disclose your information.
                    By accessing or using the Website, you agree to the terms of
                    this Policy. If you do not agree with any part of this
                    Policy, please refrain from using the Website.</span
                >
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Information Collection and Use:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        When you visit https://chark1es.dev, we may collect
                        certain non-personally identifiable information, such as
                        IP addresses and browsing patterns, for analytical
                        purposes. We may also use cookies to store certain
                        preferences, such as dark mode settings and variables,
                        to enhance your browsing experience. This data is used
                        solely for website operation and improvement.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Cloudflare and Data Usage:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        Please note that https://chark1es.dev is linked through
                        Cloudflare, a third-party service provider. Cloudflare
                        may collect and process your data in accordance with
                        their own privacy policy. This includes the collection
                        of IP addresses and other non-personal information for
                        analytical purposes or enhancing website performance. We
                        do not have control over Cloudflare's data practices and
                        encourage you to review their privacy policy.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Cloudflare Pages and Data Collection:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        https://chark1es.dev is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. As
                        such, Cloudflare may collect and process data related to
                        website usage and performance. This data is used for
                        analytics, monitoring, and optimizing website delivery.
                        Please refer to Cloudflare's privacy policy for more
                        information on how they handle data collected through
                        Cloudflare Pages.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Contact Data:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        If you choose to contact us via email, we may collect
                        your contact information, such as your name and email
                        address. We will only use this information to respond to
                        your inquiries and provide any necessary assistance. We
                        will not sell, rent, or share your contact data with any
                        third parties unless required by applicable law.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Information Security:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        We take reasonable measures to protect the
                        confidentiality and integrity of your information.
                        However, please be aware that no security system is
                        impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee the absolute
                        security of your data during transmission or storage.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Age Restriction:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal
                        information from individuals under the age of 18. If you
                        are under 18, please do not provide any personal
                        information on our website. If we become aware that we
                        have collected personal information from an individual
                        under the age of 18 without verifiable parental consent,
                        we will promptly delete that information.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-md mt-5 font-bold">
                    Changes to this Policy:
                    <div
                        class="font-normal text-sm dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                    >
                        We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at
                        any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon
                        posting on the Website. Your continued use of the
                        Website after any modifications will signify your
                        acceptance of the updated Policy.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="font-normal text-sm mt-5 dark:text-dark_mode_text_light_gray"
                >
                    If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy,
                    please contact us at contact@chark1es.org Thank you for
                    visiting https://chark1es.dev!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
